@startuml
title UC1 — Log Maintenance Request (High-Level)

actor Technician
participant "Maintenance Management System" as MMS
participant "Notification Service" as Notif
actor Supervisor

Technician -> MMS : Log maintenance request
MMS -> Notif : Send new request notification
Notif -> Supervisor : Notify new request
MMS --> Technician : Confirm request logged

@enduml